# Shared Module

Base infrastructure and abstractions shared across all modules.

## Contents

- `Contracts/` — Interface definitions for cross-module communication
- `DTOs/` — Data Transfer Objects used across module boundaries
- `Enums/` — Shared domain enums
- `Traits/` — Reusable traits for models and classes
- `Exceptions/` — Custom exception classes
- `Helpers/` — Utility functions

## Rule

The Shared module should contain **only** abstractions and utilities. Concrete implementations belong in feature modules.

Do not add business logic or domain models here.
